<tr>
<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center; padding:4pt; line-height:1.25em; text-align:center; font-size:8pt;"><a href="/wiki/File:BrunoLatour.jpg" class="image" title="BrunoLatour.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cb/BrunoLatour.jpg/180px-BrunoLatour.jpg" width="180" height="213" border="0" /></a><br />
<div style="padding-top:2pt;"><span style=""><a href="/wiki/France" title="France">French</a> <a href="/wiki/Sociology_of_science" title="Sociology of science">sociologist of science</a> and <a href="/wiki/Anthropology" title="Anthropology">anthropologist</a>. <a href="/wiki/Actor-network_theory" title="Actor-network theory">ANT</a> and <a href="/wiki/Science_and_technology_studies" title="Science and technology studies">STS</a> theorist</span></div>
</td>
</tr>
